{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, there's nothing-- is there anything in the-- show me something in law.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they worked, they did a lot of homework, but they couldn't find anything in the German law.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Two or three American lawyers of his situation had found that out-- there's nothing in the law that says that if you pass the German-- if you're a fully qualified German lawyer, and have been a German lawyer, you can ask to go back.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't want him, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They thought competition.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he really wasn't, I don't think, competition, because he developed his clientele.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He traveled all over America and told America-- and told interested people of their rights to get restitution for their-- the things they had been through.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many of them had left factories, and businesses, and had endless losses, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And those few that had survived-- no balance between these two figures, values.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But still those few that had survived, could, if they could prove this, this, this, and this, could get a certain restitution from the very well-developed-- developing West German law.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it has been a wonderful country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Kempner, many people have written to him and say, they feel he played a role by staying in Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Being brave enough to stay there in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It sometimes took quite a little bravery, you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nuremberg was not liked and-- anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Gradually, Nuremberg has become quite liked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now people are writing their doctorates on thesis concerned with Nuremberg law.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And right now, the Bosnian situation has again awakened a great interest in the Nuremberg Trials.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
